{"tid":1906860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Cloudflare (NET) 前景分析","createTime":"2020-03-02T08:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T07:28:23.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0204cd9f450cf852740c7b29c37c45eadc84afc6","tid":1906860,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>本文經刪減<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\nCloudflare reported strong results last quarter. Its growth factor was boosted by strong double-digit growth in revenue and customer count. The number of paying and large enterprise customers also grew significantly, and the dollar-based <span style=\"color: red;\">net retention rate came in at 112%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. Going forward, management is guiding for revenue growth of 41%-43%. Cloudflare is a bet of the need for web apps to deliver fast, reliable, and secure services to end-users. While this doesn't directly translate to revenue for customers like the lead generation platform offered by Facebook (FB) or Alphabet (GOOGL), the case can still be made that optimal, reliable, and secure access to web assets drives user experience which results in better customer sales conversion rates for revenue-generating platforms.<br />\n<br />\nThis means Cloudflare <span style=\"color: red;\">will continue to grow as long as it delivers on its promises to its growing clients</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. The recent performance continues to validate the thesis that Cloudflare will continue to play a key role in the current web evolution.<br />\n<img src=\"https://static2.seekingalpha.com/uploads/sa_presentations/952/51952/slides/3.jpg?1581709211\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic2.seekingalpha.com%2Fuploads%2Fsa_presentations%2F952%2F51952%2Fslides%2F3.jpg%3F1581709211&h=88a73d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRevenue is now increasingly driven by its security solutions, though the company mostly lands with its reliability and performance offerings. The incentive to cross-sell its security solution is compelling given the capability issues and switching cost of combining various vendors when deploying web assets. This incentive mostly applies to Cloudflare's customers as most companies still go with the full cybersecurity solutions of pure plays like Palo Alto (PANW), Fortinet (FTNT) and new cloud players like CrowdStrike (CRWD), and Zscaler (ZS). As it stands, <span style=\"color: red;\">Cloudflare's strength tilts towards the mid-market.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Therefore, its large enterprise-strength narrative will cause its valuation to lead growth in the near term. As a result, I am only comfortable acquiring shares on a volatility-induced correction.<br />\n<br />\nCloudflare's <span style=\"color: red;\">margins sacrifice continues to reflect its market share</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> acquisition strategy. Value investors will find it tough to make a decision on its lack of profitability. Though the path to profitability appears clear as more free users are converted to paid users. Key global traffic drivers were underplayed to drive demand during the last conference call. This includes large sporting events like the Olympics. Though, the company is guiding to sell more into the Fed space in light of the upcoming US election as parties set up security assets to thwart nation-state attacks.<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/06zN8z2.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2020/2/22/saupload_a63750b7a34cec58f1a4724a6cd3040e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.seekingalpha.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F2%2F22%2Fsaupload_a63750b7a34cec58f1a4724a6cd3040e.png&h=61e85ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nI find <span style=\"color: red;\">valuation overheated at a market cap of $6 billion</span>, given its lack of profitability and negative operating cash flow. Compared to most competitors, it is trading at a lofty sales multiple though the potential to continue its strong momentum is compelling given its strong market share acquisition momentum and reach in both the web security and content delivery space. It only has 10% of Fortune 1000 companies as paying customers, which implies the market share <span style=\"color: red;\">expansion opportunity is huge</span>.<br />\n<br />\nSummary:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4327371-cloudflare-bull-case-is-intact\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fseekingalpha.com%2Farticle%2F4327371-cloudflare-bull-case-is-intact&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igfZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=015523c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://seekingalpha.com/article/4327371-cloudflare-bull-case-is-intact</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573bf044b8c085d76e73cd4a33382883de0f7372","tid":1906860,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815a1b78a7f3c3cf38d984a62e205a9f1d81fdc3","tid":1906860,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>本文經刪減<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></div><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n此po已完"},{"pid":"e60ff20dae7e2038abfff4ec86ec3c5f82449293","tid":1906860,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"繼TSLA SPCE MSFT AMD BYND之後 連燈又有新嘅概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e8c925bed70e0b127c82040728b159de0b4d9f","tid":1906860,"uid":1059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等插"},{"pid":"36f7193877d4509c619fbb96e4ba754a7a53ea7a","tid":1906860,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e60ff20dae7e2038abfff4ec86ec3c5f82449293","tid":1906860,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"繼TSLA SPCE MSFT AMD BYND之後 連燈又有新嘅概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"你拎MSFT同其他比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 呢篇文係從基本面分析,賭仔唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4769f2d5ec0e52cc5631fa743eb3fff69099b78","tid":1906860,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3e8c925bed70e0b127c82040728b159de0b4d9f","tid":1906860,"uid":1059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等插"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"cloud security必然係未來既趨勢,<br />\n係差在搵唔搵到一隻優質既股姐,<br />\n冇人話一定係cloudflare<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb0445fd1d00c59259cee5aadce2bc792a13b70","tid":1906860,"uid":303614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"一個鐘頭前加入左watchlist，就見到樓主出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a486962074edcbdc82acb980a5c4443ba8d8f1c","tid":1906860,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"19a7fe9f7e262e231666ace13d5a1ade0deaddd1"